author: wn.com
title: Russian ambassador says Canada's fight against ISIS has been futile
text: Russia's ambassador to Canada, Alexander Darchiev, says Ottawa should align with Russia in its fight against ISIS. But Western officials say the primary purpose of Russia's military incursion in the war-torn country is bolstering the regime of brutal Syrian President Bashar al-Assad. ...
